data.title: My Chemical Romance's Frank Iero announces solo work
data.meta_description: Former My Chemical Romance guitarist, Frank Iero, revealed plans for a solo 7-inch on his website. The 7-inch will be titled for jamia... and will feature two songs. It will be available physically and digitally December 10, 2013.  My Chemical Romance broke up earlier this year....
